a2t.text_actual: A spectacular backdrop of storm clouds, lightning, and rain!   Not a movie, with full support for landscape mode and home-screen switching!  Works on both phones and tablets! If you enjoy this wallpaper, please get the full version, so we can keep making more of these.  It has a full settings screen with lots of controls for colors and behavior, including touch sensitivity, time of day, rain hitting the camera, and more! TO USE: Home->Long Press->Wallpapers
